title: Bob Dylan & Others All That Gospel
description:
Bob Dylan was inspired by several different styles in his long career as folk, country, 
rock & roll, jazz, reggae and blues.And he inspired other artists in their music....

This 3 cd selection has the spot on the religiuos inspired music..

A www.dylannl.blogspot.com production. Artwork DylanForeverman France...

Also available All That Jazz, All That Blues, All That Reggae , All That Country.....
